sans-serif&quot;; font-size: var(--font_size);">SkinTalks</span><br></h1></div></div><div data-label="Row" id="r-1596980964958" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1596980964958" style="float: none; margin: auto; display: block;" data-extraclass=""><div class="gf_col-lg-12 gf_column" id="c-1596783587877" data-id="1596783587877"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1596980964998" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1596980964998"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 670px !important; height: 156.734px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 335px 78.3672px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 670px !important; height: 156.734px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="65" height="21" style="display: none; top: 68px !important; left: 44px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-679023" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><p>Hi, and welcome to the amazing world of Korean skin care! With wide verity of skin care options, it can be hard to figure out what suits your skin best. You might also find yourself wondering&nbsp;<span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">what all the hype is about Korean skin care?&nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg); font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">Well It's time to find out!</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg); font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><br></span></p><p><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">Korean skin care has been taking over the world, and Europe&nbsp;</span><span style="background-color: var(--body_bg); color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">is no exception! In this post, we'll dive into the reasons behind the craze for Korean skin care in The Netherlands and the rest of Europe.</span></p><p><br></p></div></div><div data-label="Separator" data-key="separator" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1679061200701" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1679061200701" style="display: block;"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1653642767984" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1653642767984" data-layout-lg="12" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12" style=""><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1653642484175" data-id="1653642484175"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1671539572644" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1671539572644"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 25px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 12.5px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 26px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-5051" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">1. Innovation and technology: The key to that Glow</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1653642768106" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1653642768106"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 313.469px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 156.734px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 313px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="58" height="21" style="display: none; top: 46px !important; left: 115px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-91640" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false" data-exc=""><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif">Korean skin care is all about&nbsp;<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 241, 229);">innovation and technology</span>, and that's the secret to that glowing skin you've been seeing all over Instagram. These Brands are always one step ahead when it comes to the latest research in skin care. This results in developing new formulas and techniques to tackle a wide range of skin concerns.&nbsp;</font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p><font face="Poppins, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif">When Korean skin care brands revamp their formulations this also helps to keep their products <span style="background-color: rgb(255, 241, 229);">original and unique</span>.&nbsp;Staying on top of their formulations and ensuring that their products are authentic, Korean skin care brands can maintain their reputation for high-quality, effective skincare products.</font></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" id="r-1679403978807" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1679403978807" style="float: none; margin: auto; display: block;" data-extraclass=""><div class="gf_col-lg-12 gf_column" id="c-1596783587877" data-id="1596783587877"><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1679403978794" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1679403978794" data-layout-lg="8+4" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="8+4" data-layout-sm="8+4" data-layout-xs="8+4"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-8 gf_col-md-8 gf_col-sm-8 gf_col-xs-8" id="c-1653642484175" data-id="1653642484175"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1679403978783" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1679403978783"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 25px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 12.5px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 26px !important;"></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-5051" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">2. Unique ingredients: Snail Mucin, Centella & Ginseng, oh my!</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1679403978742" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1679403978742"><lt-highlighter contenteditable="false" class="lt--mac-os" data-lt-linked="1" style="display: none; z-index: auto !important;"><lt-div spellcheck="false" class="lt-highlighter__wrapper" style="width: 593.328px !important; height: 313.469px !important; transform: none !important; transform-origin: 296.664px 156.734px !important; zoom: 1 !important;"><lt-div class="lt-highlighter__scroll-element" style="top: 0px !important; left: 0px !important; width: 593px !important; height: 313px !important;"><canvas class="lt-highlighter__canvas" width="58" height="21" style="display: none; top: 46px !important; left: 115px !important;"></canvas></lt-div></lt-div></lt-highlighter><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-91640" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false" data-exc=""><p><br></p><p>Korean skin care is also known for using unique and exotic ingredients that aren't commonly found in Western skincare products. Yup, <span style="font-weight: bold;">Snail Mucin</span> is a thing, and it's a game-changer. Snail&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">Mucin is a sticky substance that snails produce to protect their skin from environmental damage. And guess what? It's also incredibly beneficial for human skin! Snail Mucin contains a variety of skin-loving ingredients, such as </span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 241, 229);">Glycolic</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 241, 229);"> Acid, Hyaluronic Acid, and Peptides</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">, that can help with skin </span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 241, 229);">regeneration, hydration, and overall skin health</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">.</span></p><p><br></p><p>Another unique ingredient commonly used in Korean skin care is <span style="font-weight: bold;">Centella Asiatica</span>, also known as tiger grass. This plant also has been used for centuries in traditional Chinese medicine to heal wounds and soothe irritated skin. It has <span style="background-color: rgb(255, 241, 229);">anti-inflammatory and antioxidant properties</span>, making it great for sensitive or inflamed skin. You'll often find Centella Asiatica in&nbsp;<span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">creams and serums, to help soothe and heal the skin.</span></p><p><br></p><p>The next fun, unique ingredient commonly found in Korean skin care is <span style="font-weight: bold;">Ginseng</span>. This powerful root extract is known for its <span style="background-color: rgb(255, 241, 229);">anti-aging and anti-inflammatory properties</span>, making it a popular ingredient in many anti-aging skin care products. Ginseng is used to <span style="background-color: rgb(255, 241, 229);">increase collagen production, improve skin elasticity, and even out skin tone</span>. Additionally, Ginseng is rich in antioxidants, which help to protect the skin from damage caused by free radicals. With many extraordinary, benefits, it's no wonder that rarer ingredients have become a stable in Korean skin care products.</p><p><br></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-4 gf_col-md-4 gf_col-sm-4 gf_col-xs-4" id="c-1682426239690" data-id="1682426239690"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1682426258599" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1682426258599" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/4ada2379-3680-491c-b69d-0279c665c389/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/snail-mucin.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" width="800" height="800" data-width="130px" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="800" natural-height="800"></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1682426255816" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1682426255816" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/63bc9851-186f-461a-b1c0-aca7e5efdd67/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/centella-asiatica.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" width="800" height="800" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="800" natural-height="800"></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1682426261240" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1682426261240" data-resolut